headline: FedEx Award Highlights Circular Push Blockchain Entry And InPost Expansion
summary: FedEx (NYSE:FDX) received the 2025 Circular Economy Leadership Award for its e-waste logistics pilot. The company launched the Circular Supply Chain Coalition to advance circular economy practices across logistics. FedEx is co-leading a €7.8b consortium bid to acquire InPost, a major European parcel network.
